{"image_id": "SYK_2010_page_60", "image_size": [1275, 1650], "ocr": [{"text": "The Company’s stock based plans include stock options, restricted stock units and employee stock", "bbox": [204.2, 159.1, 1026.0, 179.9]}, {"text": "purchases. The following is a summary of the Company’s significant stock compensation plans:", "bbox": [162.5, 184.1, 964.1, 204.9]}, {"text": "Stock Options", "bbox": [162.5, 246.4, 278.9, 267.2]}, {"text": "The Company has key employee and director stock option plans under which options are granted at an", "bbox": [204.2, 284.1, 1059.4, 304.9]}, {"text": "exercise price not less than the fair market value of the underlying common stock at the date of grant. The", "bbox": [162.5, 309.1, 1047.2, 329.9]}, {"text": "options are granted for periods of up to 10 years and become exercisable in varying installments. A summary of", "bbox": [162.5, 334.1, 1096.3, 354.9]}, {"text": "stock option activity follows:", "bbox": [162.5, 359.1, 406.5, 379.9]}, {"text": "Shares", "bbox": [642.0, 437.1, 690.1, 453.7]}, {"text": "(in millions)", "bbox": [623.4, 453.7, 709.0, 470.4]}, {"text": "Weighted", "bbox": [745.9, 420.4, 814.5, 437.1]}, {"text": "Average", "bbox": [750.5, 437.1, 809.8, 453.7]}, {"text": "Exercise Price", "bbox": [729.6, 453.7, 830.9, 470.4]}, {"text": "Weighted-Average", "bbox": [851.7, 403.7, 985.0, 420.4]}, {"text": "Remaining", "bbox": [879.4, 420.4, 957.2, 437.1]}, {"text": "Contractual Term", "bbox": [853.2, 437.1, 983.2, 453.7]}, {"text": "(in years)", "bbox": [884.8, 453.7, 951.8, 470.4]}, {"text": "Aggregate", "bbox": [1022.5, 420.4, 1095.6, 437.1]}, {"text": "Intrinsic Value", "bbox": [1005.7, 437.1, 1112.5, 453.7]}, {"text": "(in millions)", "bbox": [1016.5, 453.7, 1102.1, 470.4]}, {"text": "Options outstanding at January 1, 2010 . . . . . . . . . .", "bbox": [162.5, 484.1, 602.6, 504.9]}, {"text": "26.3", "bbox": [647.9, 484.1, 684.4, 504.9]}, {"text": "$45.69", "bbox": [751.6, 484.1, 808.9, 504.9]}, {"text": "Granted . . . . .